10 oddball American rock classics

Download or stream these psychedelic classics for free. All you’ll need is you library card and PIN.

  1. Looser for you Baby: Dr John from American Legend Vol. 1
  2. Monk Time: The Monks from The Early Years 1964 -1965
  3. Levitation: The 13th Floor Elevators from The Psychedelic World Of
  4. You Yesyesyes Again: The Residents from Fingerprince
  5. Skunk (Sonically Speaking): MC5 from The Anthology 1965–1971
  6. Sure ‘Nuff ‘N Yes I Do: Captain Beefheart and the Magic Band from The Buddah Years
  7. Mustang Sally: Silver Apples from The Garden
  8. In-A-Gadda-Da-Vida (full album version): Iron Butterfly from In-A-Gadda-Da-Vida
  9. Dixie Chicken (Live): Little Feat from Hellzapoppin
  10. Walkin’ Blues: Hot Tuna from Original Album Classics
